{"tid":1170653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日笑一笑】猩猩怕大雨 靠牆簷篷底避雨","createTime":"2019-05-25T06:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T06:51:42.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9c257e40a1772f7acc25ca83e6f475d9618fab54","tid":1170653,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"落大雨不只人會避雨，猩猩也會。<br />\n<br />\n外國一個動物園內的猩猩，集體躲在簷篷下避雨，但途中其中一隻按捺不住，沿着狹窄的簷篷底跑到另一面。<br />\n另外兩隻猩猩見狀，考慮一會後，也按此方法跑走。最後一隻猩猩見牠們全跑走後，也決定跟隨大隊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【今日笑一笑】猩猩怕大雨 靠牆簷篷底避雨<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190525&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59635588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190525%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59635588&d=QgRa2nBc7vcC6sJiZdE62JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=5f4f4231\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190525%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59635588&h=349490e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190525&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59635588</a>"},{"pid":"f97a534364394c763094b964ae727949e3d34e67","tid":1170653,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T06:51:42.000Z","msg":"打工仔出去食飯冇帶遮但突然落大雨嘅寫照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}